575
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:57,603
I'm not afraid of the Israelis.

576
00:34:57,662 --> 00:35:00,404
Believe me, I've been in hairier situations.

577
00:35:00,966 --> 00:35:02,206
Cave off of Maui.

578
00:35:02,267 --> 00:35:07,012
That's a walk in the park. I once had a
parachute pack refuse to open at 15,000 feet.

579
00:35:07,072 --> 00:35:10,417
I opened it with a pen
knife, 3,000 feet to spare.

580
00:35:10,775 --> 00:35:12,379
Don't you get scared?

581
00:35:13,244 --> 00:35:15,315
You know, like most people?

582
00:35:16,748 --> 00:35:17,886
You know...

583
00:35:19,884 --> 00:35:22,057
I mean, you don't get scared at all?

584
00:35:23,622 --> 00:35:25,124
I wonder why?

585
00:35:25,690 --> 00:35:26,862
It's a gift.

586
00:35:28,326 --> 00:35:31,170
It allows me to push myself
harder than other people.

587
00:35:31,229 --> 00:35:35,302
You can always trick yourself into
believing that you're invincible.

588
00:35:35,867 --> 00:35:39,178
If somebody tags me with a laser
sight, I'm gonna keep going.

589
00:35:43,408 --> 00:35:45,046
Your wife, Kerry,

590
00:35:47,879 --> 00:35:50,018
