591
00:35:51,149 --> 00:35:53,686
Because of your self-confidence?

592
00:35:53,785 --> 00:35:55,423
You'll have to ask her.

593
00:35:55,787 --> 00:35:57,289
I'll tell you this,

594
00:35:58,556 --> 00:36:01,298
