out of bed in the morning.

595
00:36:05,630 --> 00:36:07,405
She's my prayer warrior.

596
00:36:11,369 --> 00:36:13,645
She believes in you. It's important.

597
00:36:14,339 --> 00:36:16,444
She knows I'll never let her down.

598
00:36:19,811 --> 00:36:21,757
You wanna know how she's doing?

599
00:36:23,014 --> 00:36:24,652
Cause we can...

600
00:36:24,983 --> 00:36:26,724
Come on.

601
00:36:29,521 --> 00:36:32,365
