have anything to do with anything.

603
00:36:38,196 --> 00:36:39,231
I wanna talk to her.

604
00:36:39,297 --> 00:36:42,437
Since you're under arrest,
Mr. Harris, I can't allow it.

605
00:36:43,735 --> 00:36:46,579
But I can see her. I'm allowed to talk to her.

606
00:36:50,008 --> 00:36:52,750
If there's anything that
you need to say to her,

607
00:36:53,478 --> 00:36:55,685
you know, give her your love or...

608
00:37:01,653 --> 00:37:03,496
How's my husband? When can I see him?

609
00:37:03,555 --> 00:37:06,092
It shouldn't be much longer.

610
00:37:06,157 --> 00:37:08,535
Your son's really liking those cartoons.

611
00:37:09,094 --> 00:37:11,199
He's a very active child.

612
00:37:13,898 --> 00:37:17,402
Just like his Dad, huh?
With all that scuba diving,

613
00:37:17,469 --> 00:37:19,073
jumping out of planes.

614
00:37:19,671 --> 00:37:21,275
It's a thrill a minute.

615
00:37:22,741 --> 00:37:24,880
He trained hard to do those things.

616
00:37:27,178 --> 00:37:29,351
Kid stays with you. That's smart.

617
00:37:30,181 --> 00:37:31,888
Anything happens to Kenny,

618
00:37:32,016 --> 00:37:34,496
his parachute doesn't open
or he runs out of...

619
00:37:34,552 --> 00:37:36,361
